                Hardworking and knowledgeable web developer and instructor with <strong>8 years of experience</strong> in software 
                development and education. Expertise in <strong>C#</strong>, <strong>ASP.NET</strong>, and <strong>agile methodologies</strong>, 
                with a proven track record of mentoring students and leading curriculum design.
            </p>
            <p>
                Successfully transitioned teams to agile practices and developed robust web applications, enhancing performance and 
                user experience. My work spans <strong>full-stack development</strong>, <strong>systems programming</strong>, 
                <strong>DevOps</strong>, <strong>database engineering</strong>, and <strong>cloud infrastructure</strong>. 
                I regularly work with modern frameworks, CI/CD pipelines, relational and non-relational databases, and UNIX-based systems.
            </p>
            <p>
